Module jakarta.persistence
Package jakarta.persistence

Annotation Type NamedNativeQuery

@Repeatable(NamedNativeQueries.class) @Target(TYPE) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface NamedNativeQuery
Specifies a named native SQL query and, optionally, the mapping of the result of the native SQL query. Query names are scoped to the persistence unit. The NamedNativeQuery annotation can be applied to an entity or mapped superclass.
Since:
1.0
